
Overview of noun penalty

The noun penalty has 4 senses (first 3 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (6) punishment, penalty, penalization, penalisation -- (the act of punishing)
2. (1) penalty -- (a payment required for not fulfilling a contract)
3. (1) penalty -- (the disadvantage or painful consequences of an action or condition; "neglected his health and paid the penalty")
4. penalty -- ((games) a handicap or disadvantage that is imposed on a competitor (or a team) for an infraction of the rules of the game)
